commit.message:
Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/isaykatsman/learnmysites

Conflicts:
	index.html
	js/kmeans.js
	js/scraper.js
Lowered limit on min articles per tab

Fixed nearly all bugs with live aggregator, working properly. Most missing little features have been implemented. Still remaining to do the checkboxes for RSS feeds, progress bar, user interest based link serving.
Fixed some issues with feed serve.
Added a get cluster names method and also a way to serve JS live.
Merged two repos (Horace He + Isay Katsman)

Added a demo page, cleaned up parts of main page. Made feed elements
links.
Added working k-means and tSNE embeddings to web view.
Added D3 graphs that will serve as article embeddings.
Initial commit. Simply installed some starter files.
